70b14f6e5765"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "In our setting, Schur-Weyl duality provides a clean way to bookkeep irrep \
multiplicity in the input space ",
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox["X", TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "d303d57a-8c9b-4740-94e7-67872f48e8f9"],
 "."
}], "Text",
