Cell["\<\
Allowing for arbitrary rearrangements of the tensor product, we have\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.972143670453368*^9, 3.972143735300456*^9}, {
   3.972143786963975*^9, 3.972143795155884*^9}, {3.972143858372986*^9, 
